snippet.title: iAssociate 2 for the iPhone, iPad and iPod Touch!
snippet.description:
iAssociate is a word association game by TicBits. In iAssociate, your goal is to guess words that are associated to the already given words.

For example, what words do you associate Breakfast with? Maybe Eggs, or Coffee?

iAssociate 2 is FREE to download and comes with hours of brain sharpening levels, with even more levels available for purchase for you who fall in love with it. Download it now from iTunes!

For more information visit: http://iassociate2.ticbits.com/
